---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import TimeLineElement from "../components/cv/TimeLine.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Resume" sideBarActiveItemID="cv">
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Profile</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10 text-justify">
    Software Engineer with a strong background in Front End fundamentals, looking for new opportunities to promote personal growth and continuous learning, whilst creating impact and making a difference. 🚀
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Education</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container grid gap-4 mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="const college = true;"
      subtitle="경희대학교 컴퓨터공학부 (Kyung Hee University, School of Computing), Seoul, South Korea"
    />
    <TimeLineElement
      title="college += 1;"
      subtitle="University of the People (UoPeople), Pasadena, CA"
    />
    <TimeLineElement
      title="return college ++;"
      subtitle="University of Arizona (UofA), Tucson, AZ"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Experience</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Full Stack Web Developer"
      subtitle="Easton Nights Inc., New York, NY"
    >
    <div class="font-bold w-full mb-2 mt-2">Seo Optimization and Performance Enhancements:</div>
    Accelerated site performance by 20% through the implementation of the Astro framework static build package, optimizing site-loading speed, component loading speed, and static asset loading, resulting in elevated search engine rankings and a 80% reduction in page load times for an enhanced user experience.
    <div class="font-bold w-full mb-2 mt-2">Web Development and Modernization:</div>
    Revitalized an outdated website and refactored the codebase for Astro compatibility, incorporating React components, transitioning legacy React class components into modern functional components following SOLID principles, and securing HTTPS access and improving overall website efficiency through the successful implementation of Axios, ensuring code quality and maintainability.
    </TimeLineElement>
  <br>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Director of Experience"
      subtitle="Hakkasan Group, Las Vegas, NV"
    >
    <div class="font-bold w-full mb-2 mt-2">Critical Marketing and Event Management:</div>
    Developed and executed strategic marketing and promotional campaigns for Omnia, Jewel, and Hakkasan, doubling patron attendance during peak periods while orchestrating cross-functional teams in event logistics, production, and entertainment, leading to a remarkable 98% growth in customer satisfaction ratings over a 5-year period.
    <div class="font-bold w-full mb-2 mt-2">Strategic Relationship Building for Revenue Growth:</div>
    Utilized social engineering techniques and held customer development seminars for all employees to cultivate relationships with key partners, vendors, and clients, contributing to a substantial 40% increase in quarterly revenue.
    </TimeLineElement>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Certifications</div>
  </div>

  <ul class="list-disc mx-6 mb-10 grid gap-2">
    <li>
      Javascript Algorithms and Data Structures (FCC)
    </li>
    <li>
      IBM Full Stack Cloud Engineering
    </li>
    <li>
      Certified Ethical Hacking (CEH in progress)
    </li>
    <li>
      AWS Cloud Associate Certifications (in progress)
    </li>
    <li>
      Python (PCEP, PCAP, PCPP)
    </li>
  </ul>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Skills</div>
  </div>

  <ul class="list-disc md:columns-5 columns-2 mx-6 mb-10">
    <li>Javascript</li>
    <li>React</li>
    <li>HTML/CSS</li>
    <li>Astro</li>
    <li>Tailwind</li>
    <li>Python</li>
    <li>Git</li>
    <li>Cloud Dev.</li>
    <li>Postman</li>
    <li>API</li>
    <li>Front-End Dev.</li>
    <li>Sec Ops</li>
    <li>Leadership</li>
    <li>Creativity</li>
    <li>Problem-Solving</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Contact</div>
  </div>

  <ul class="list-disc mx-6 grid gap-2">
    <li>
      📱 (610) 905-1376
    </li>
    <li>
      📧 LinkLokiLee@proton.me
    </li>
  </ul>
</BaseLayout>
